Package: rtemis.draw
Title: Interactive Visualization Using ECharts
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person(given = "E.D.", family = "Gennatas", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email = "gennatas@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9280-3609"))
Description: Provides a comprehensive R interface to Apache ECharts
    (<https://echarts.apache.org>) for creating interactive charts and
    visualizations. Offers type-checked, validated configuration objects
    built with S7 classes that mirror the ECharts TypeScript API, with
    convenience functions for common chart types and full htmlwidgets
    integration for use in Quarto, Shiny, and IDE viewers.
